<div id="review_1258023663" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1258023663" />
    <a title="Mario Tomic" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18944510-mario-tomic"><img alt="Mario Tomic" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1528799694p2/18944510.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1258023663?book_show_action=true">Jan 30, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mario Tomic" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mario Tomic" href="/user/show/18944510-mario-tomic">Mario Tomic</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1258023663" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15725800532556568337">This is one of my favorite books on how the human brain works. It exposes all the weaknesses we have in our thinking process, helps break down things we consider &quot;normal&quot;, and much much more. Very good material, highly recommended!</span>
  <span id="freeText15725800532556568337" style="display:none">This is one of my favorite books on how the human brain works. It exposes all the weaknesses we have in our thinking process, helps break down things we consider "normal", and much much more. Very good material, highly recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="15725800532556568337" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

