<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/125966.Choices_Values_and_Frames"><img alt="Choices, Values, and Frames" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1384187634l/125966._SX98_.jpg" />
